194
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:06,400
And I think over the span of like spamming her on Twitter over the entire PyCon weekend, I finally got her to sign up.

195
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:12,400
And now she's doing a phenomenal, not that she wasn't before, but she's continued to be doing phenomenal things.

196
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:16,400
And she's a community service recipient, has helped start PyCon Africa.

197
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:24,400
The PyCon African communities have been so instrumental, I think, in showing, again, a different perspective that we may not have otherwise seen.

